# Config Layer

`src/config/` berisi wiring third-party dan cross-cutting concerns.

## Environment Config

Semua env variable diakses via `ConfigModule` + `configuration.ts`:

```typescript
// src/config/env/configuration.ts
export default () => ({
    app: { port: parseInt(process.env.PORT, 10) || 3000 },
    database: { url: process.env.DATABASE_URL }
})
```

Akses di service/main via `ConfigService`:

```typescript
const port = config.get<number>('app.port', { infer: true }) ?? 3000
```

Jangan akses `process.env` langsung di luar `configuration.ts`.

## Prisma Setup

- `PrismaService` extends `PrismaClient` — inject `ConfigService` untuk DB URL
- `PrismaModule` harus `@Global()` agar semua feature bisa inject tanpa import ulang
- Prisma client import dari `@prisma/generated/client`
- Adapter: `@prisma/adapter-mariadb` (MySQL/MariaDB)

```typescript
@Global()
@Module({ providers: [PrismaService], exports: [PrismaService] })
export class PrismaModule {}
```

## Exception Filter

- `NotFoundExceptionFilter` catch `PrismaClientKnownRequestError`
- `P2025` → HTTP 404 dengan `{ statusCode, message }`
- Register sebagai global filter di `main.ts`: `app.useGlobalFilters(new NotFoundExceptionFilter())`

## App Module

Global pipes/interceptors di `AppModule.providers`:

```typescript
providers: [
    { provide: APP_PIPE, useClass: ZodValidationPipe },
    { provide: APP_INTERCEPTOR, useClass: ZodSerializerInterceptor }
]
```

Feature modules ditambahkan di `AppModule.imports`.
